    function like(item){
    let parent=item.parentNode.parentNode.parentNode;
    if(parent.isLiked){
    item.style.color = "#191919";
    parent.isLiked = false;
    }
    else {
    item.style.color = "#ec4b4b";
    parent.isLiked = true;
    }
    }
